)
</caption>
</image>

Hopkins was married and divorced four times: first to actor <link>
Brandon Peters</link>, second to aviator <link>
Austin Parker</link>, third to the director <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../134/1566134.xml">
Anatole Litvak</link>, and fourth to war correspondent <link>
Raymond B. Brock</link>. In 1932, Hopkins adopted a son, Michael Hopkins. </p>
<p>

Hopkins died in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../042/645042.xml">
New York, New York</link> from a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../969/60969.xml">
heart attack</link> nine days before her 70th birthday.</p>
<p>

